Interface GetRealTimeUserInputFieldsInterface


  • public interface GetRealTimeUserInputFieldsInterface
    Supports to get the definition and the value of all real-time user input fields from a running load test job.
    Since:
    Proxy Sniffer V5.2-P

    • Method Detail

      • getRealTimeUserInputFields

        java.util.ArrayList<RealTimeUserInputField> getRealTimeUserInputFields()
        Get the definition and the value of all real-time user input fields.
        Returns:
        the definition and the value of all real-time user input fields, or null if this method fails. Note: if no real-time user input fields are defined then an empty array list is returned.
